{"tid":1386451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門屋苑業主清理門戶！動議罷免顧問後 何君堯辭職","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T10:49:32.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c78bb560d913b218fa0ac690b309ce16f2ac4ee8","tid":1386451,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:49:32.000Z","msg":"建制派立法會議員何君堯被拍到，在元朗7.21恐襲當晚，與被指黑幫的白衣暴徒握手，更大讚對方做得好，是保鄉衞族的「衞士」，向牠們高舉拇指；早前更於facebook直播，揚言元朗六鄉人「密啲手，將佢（外來者）打到去片甲不留」，引起全城公憤。何君堯本身亦擔任屯門大興花園第二期的義務法律顧問，有業主要求法團罷免何。法團管理委員原訂下周三（8月7日）投票表決，惟何在通告公佈後5日、今日（7月30日）向法團率先辭任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190730/59879012?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190730%2F59879012%3F&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=100bd465\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190730%2F59879012%3F&h=cd669bd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190730/59879012?</a>"}]}